<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HE LIVES</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa hing na ka sem, tun khawvel ah A um,
 A hing hi tih ka hei, min bang cheng gen mahleu le;
 A hehpih khut ka mui, A lungmuon aw gi ka zai,
 Ka ngaih cheng leh ka kawmah a hung nai zing hi.

[V2]
 A hing, A hing, Krista tunin A hing,
 Ei kitawnpih in ei hopih, hinna lampi chipah;
 A hing, A hing; hukdamna mi pie di'n,
 Bangti'n na he'm? tih nei dawt leh,
 Ka lungsung ah A hing.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel muntin chengah Aman ei enkawl ka hei,
 Ka lunggil lungkham sek mahleh lungdawng ngei puong ka;
 Huihpi leh guohpi nuoiah eipui hi tih ka he'i,
 Atawp leh A hung kilatni hungtung ina.

[V4]
 3. Lawpin, lawpin aw Kristien, kipak takin la sa'n,
 Lalpen Krista chu kumsawta chawihat in um hen;
 Amah hawlte kinepna, Amute Panpihpa,
 Mi lungsiet, Pha leh zainem amah bang umlo.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>136</hymn_number>
</song>